director.name: 杰里·西科里蒂 Jerry Ciccoritti

introduction: QUEEN BEE and BABY DYNAMITE, a masked tag-team. One of their opponents dies in the ring. The dead wrestler's fiancé orders hit man team JOHN BOSCO and MARIE after the fighters. The girls survive many roadside adventures. Queen Bee and Baby Dynamite stumble out of the Mexican desert and onto a decaying Hacienda to discover the owners are hostage to the evil DON EMILIO, cursed to live as a CHUPACABRA monster, and his ZOMBIE army. The luchadoras meet EL CHARRO ENMASCARADO, a Zorro-type whose mission is to kill the Chupacabra. But it will only work if they convince the hit men to join them.
